high_descs: Turn left and go along the wall toward the fridge. Turn right at the fridge and go forward until you come to the stove.
Pick up the skillet from the back left burner of the stove.
Turn around to your left and go back to the fridge. Turn right to fact the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the skillet on the top right shelf, with the handle pointing to the right and close the fridge.
Take the skillet back out of the fridge, turn right and carry it to the stove.
Put the skillet on the left front burner of the stove, with its handle pointing away from you.
anns.task_desc: Move a skillet from the stove to the fridge to the stove.

high_descs: Turn left and move toward the refrigerator in the corner of the room then turn right and move to the oven on the other side of the room.
Pick up the pan from the oven's back left burner.
Turn around and move towards the refrigerator in the corner then turn right and face the refrigerator.

Open the refrigerator and place the pan on the left side of the top shelf. Close the refrigerator, wait, open the refrigerator again and pick up the pan from the shelf and then close the refrigerator door.
Turn around and move towards the table in the center of the kitchen then turn left and move to the oven.
Place the pan down on the front left burner of the oven.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pan on an oven burner.

high_descs: Take a left and walk towards the refrigerator, then turn right and walk to the stove.
Pick up the pan from the stove.
Turn around and walk to the fridge on your right.
Put the pan into the fridge and wait for it to cool, then take it back out.
Turn right and walk to the stove.
Put the pan on the left, front burner.
anns.task_desc: Cool the pan in the fridge.
